, \"rank\": 5.522339545527826e-06, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her historic achievement at the Paris Olympics has sparked a wave of admiration and congratulatory messages from the Indian film industry.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 469, \"end\": 489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bollywood\", \"score\": 0.9999999907354322, \"rank\": 9.264667595612964e-09, \"text\": \"Indian film industry\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bollywood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bollywood\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Phogat's remarkable journey to the final has not gone unnoticed.\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Renowned actor RajKummar Rao took to Instagram to express his joy, sharing a photo of Phogat with a heartfelt message: \\\"We are in the finals!\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajkummar_Rao\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RajKummar Rao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajkummar_Rao\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rajkummar_Rao\"}, {\"begin\": 594, \"end\": 603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1352082113381298e-25, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 643, \"end\": 649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was such a joy to watch you live.\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are the pride of our nation, @vineshphogat.\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Good luck in the finals.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our prayers are with you.\\\"\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  Wrestler Vinesh Phogat won her semifinal bout in the Women's 50 kg freestyle category with a 5-0 victory over Cuba's Yusneylys Guzm\\u00e1n, securing a place in the finals and guaranteeing at least a#silvermedalfor India.#Olympics#OlympicGames#Olympic2024#ParisOlympics2024\\u2026pic.twitter.com/tMoP0E2eal    Advertisement  - The Statesman (@TheStatesmanLtd)August 6, 2024    Similarly, Ayushmann Khurana posted on Instagram Stories, celebrating Phogat's emotional victory over the world's top-ranked champion.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 1351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999245734741694, \"rank\": 7.31677677212178e-05, \"text\": \"Cuba\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba_national_baseball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 969, \"end\": 985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yusneylys_Guzm\\u00e1n\", \"score\": 0.9999999998694875, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yusneylys Guzm\\u00e1n\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yusneylys_Guzm\\u00e1n\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yusneylys_Guzm\\u00e1n\"}, {\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayushmann_Khurrana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ayushmann Khurana\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayushmann_Khurrana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayushmann_Khurrana\"}, {\"begin\": 1256, \"end\": 1273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Instagram Stories\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 1287, \"end\": 1293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His story read, \\\"Indian wrestler Vinesh Phogat could not stop crying after her win against the unbeatable world No.1 champion.\\\"\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\", \"score\": 0.9999936266243196, \"rank\": 5.522339545527826e-06, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He punctuated his message with a National Flag emoji.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Riteish Deshmukh also praised Phogat's performance, writing on X, \\\"That's what a champion looks like after beating the World No.1 and defending Olympic Gold Medal holder.\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1535, \"end\": 1551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riteish_Deshmukh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Riteish Deshmukh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riteish_Deshmukh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riteish_Deshmukh\"}, {\"begin\": 1565, \"end\": 1571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"#VineshPhogat.\\\"\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Taapsee Pannu shared a video of Phogat's winning moment, marveling at her accomplishment.\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pannu wrote, \\\"This woman will be remembered as a benchmark for decades!\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What a performance!\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@vineshphogat, you have earned a fan for life.\\\"\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Randeep Hooda joined in the celebrations with a post on X, featuring a photo of Phogat post-victory and a \\\"fingers crossed\\\" emoji, while Kunal Kemmu expressed his pride with, \\\"What a champ.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2034, \"end\": 2040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}, {\"begin\": 2091, \"end\": 2102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kunal_Khemu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kunal Kemmu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kunal_Khemu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kunal_Khemu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ufff.\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sooooooo Proud!!!\\\"\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His wife, who also watched the match, added, \\\"First Indian woman to reach an Olympic wrestling final, Vinesh Phogat!!!!!\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2221, \"end\": 2227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\", \"score\": 0.9999936266243196, \"rank\": 5.522339545527826e-06, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Soooo proud!!!!\\\"\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Phogat's path to the finals was nothing short of extraordinary.\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2308, \"end\": 2314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the quarter-finals, she faced Tokyo 2020 champion Yui Susaki from Japan.\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2405, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999998472049, \"rank\": 1.5279255058138121e-10, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2425, \"end\": 2435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Susaki\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yui Susaki\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Susaki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Susaki\"}, {\"begin\": 2441, \"end\": 2446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9997174615779415, \"rank\": 0.00018060277956853514, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite trailing 1-0 after the first period, Phogat made a stunning comeback in the second period, defeating Susaki 3-2 and ending her opponent's 82-match unbeaten streak.\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2493, \"end\": 2499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the semi-finals, Phogat went up against Ukraine's Oksana Livach.\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2664, \"end\": 2671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9939107250796988, \"rank\": 0.006126510001732825, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 2674, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oksana_Livach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oksana Livach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oksana_Livach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oksana_Livach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She took an early 2-0 lead and managed to hold off Livach's efforts in the second period, securing her spot in the final.\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As she prepares to face USA's Ann Sarah Hildebrandt in the final on August 7, the entire nation, along with the Indian film fraternity, eagerly awaits to cheer her on.\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2836, \"end\": 2839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.8828652718431611, \"rank\": 0.1326045486356992, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2846, \"end\": 2863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarah Hildebrandt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\"}, {\"begin\": 2924, \"end\": 2935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bollywood\", \"score\": 0.9999999495107671, \"rank\": 5.0489105781871305e-08, \"text\": \"Indian film\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bollywood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bollywood\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  India's top pistol shooters Manu Bhaker and Esha Singh endured heartbreak in the women's 10m air pistol final at the International Shooting Sport Federation (ISSF) World Championship Rifle/Pistol in Cairo on Monday, both missing out on individual medals after promising starts.\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 3275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2998, \"end\": 3003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999970410620457, \"rank\": 2.0871931817542124e-06,